7
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,672
Hello.

8
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:07,916
Yes, this is Mr. Tony Ryder.

9
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:11,352
He did?

10
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:14,710
When?

11
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,712
I see.

