203
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:24,192
Sam, he went out in style.

204
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,272
Katie! Hi!

205
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,235
Hello, Marge.

206
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:08,874
Welcome back
to the decompression chamber.

207
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:12,231
- Well, how was Palm Beach?
- It was all right, I guess.

208
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:15,910
All right? Is that all you've gotta say?
