223
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,750
But, honey, I am a doctor.
It's nothing serious.

224
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:04,349
Just something I picked up
from one of my patients.

225
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,551
- How was Florida?
- Oh, it was all right.

226
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:09,672
- But I'm glad I'm back.
- So am I.

227
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:11,632
And so will Mom and Dad be.

228
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:15,549
- Oh, yourfolks are in town?
