229
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:18,274
They can't wait to meet you.

230
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:22,112
- Well, I hope they like me.
- They'll love you.

231
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,711
Oh, well, that makes me feel better.

232
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:29,471
How about the four of us getting
together, say, Wednesday night?

233
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:33,630
Oh, that's fine. Fine.
I'd love to.

234
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:35,956
- I'll see you then.
- Goodbye, dear.

235
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,519
Bye.

